commit.message: Fix java compiler options. Removed the dependency to scala-library.jar
Add a case when encountered EOF
Use IOException in BufferedScanner. Subsequent changes to JSONLexer
Use optional class to hold color output state
Use CharSequence in the interface of BufferedScanner
Allow alnum as a single word in natural name
Add a template code for Matrix representation of a graph
Add Alnum class for representing chr1, chr2, chr10, etc.
BufferedScanner optimization for fixed length input
Removed line count feature from BufferedScanner, since it incurs overhead
Using a common interface for CharBuffer and ByteBuffer
BufferedScanner.nextLine() is now faster than BufferedReader.readLine()
use if statement instead of switch
Count line and char position in BufferedScanner
